README for Lab::Connection
-----------------------------------------------------------------------


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Build.PL
   perl Build
   perl Build install

DEPENDENCIES

This package requires these other modules and libraries:

  Lab::Bus
  Lab::Exception
  Module::Build
  Time::HiRes

